org.picocontainer
Class PicoBuilder

java.lang.Object
  org.picocontainer.PicoBuilder

public class PicoBuilder
extends Object

Helps assembles the myriad items available to a picocontainer.

Simple Example:

 MutablePicoContainer mpc = new PicoBuilder()
   .withCaching()
   .withLifecycle()
   .build();

Author:
Paul Hammant
